title: 1921–22 Isthmian League
text:
The 1921–22 season was the 13th in the history of the <a href="Isthmian%20League">Isthmian League</a>, an English <a href="Association%20football">football</a> competition.
<a href="Wimbledon%20F.C.">Wimbledon</a> and <a href="Wycombe%20Wanderers%20F.C.">Wycombe Wanderers</a> were newly admitted. <a href="Ilford%20F.C.">Ilford</a> were champions for the second season in a row, winning their third Isthmian League title.
